Nollywood actor Kenneth Okonkwo has been decorated with an award as a Goodwill Ambassador by the National Council for Women Societies Nigeria. Okonkwo shared the news on his social media handles on June 13 saying that the award is dedicated to all strong women. He wrote, “To God be the glory! I was decorated with the award of Goodwill Ambassador for all Nigerian women by the National Council for Women Societies Nigeria.” “Women are the heartbeat of the society, the birth Kings and wear the crown of glory no wonder they are recognized as “The Queen” even in the game of chess. They are my heroes.” He further stated, “This award is dedicated to all the strong women that follow me here, I love you all.”